{{Top|leg}}
A '''B23-1-14 permit''' was required to be submitted when collecting a [[Bounty/Legends|bounty]]. Submission of a valid permit enabled a [[Bounty hunter/Legends|bounty hunter]] to collect all local, [[Star system/Legends|system]], [[Sector/Legends|sector]], and regional bounties as reward for a successful hunt.<ref name="Bounty Hunters' Guild Handbook article">{{InsiderCite|99|Bounty Hunters' Guild Handbook (article)}}</ref>

[[Sammie Staable]] once attempted to collect the bounty for capturing [[Ten-Suckers Madoom]] without a valid permit, and only received the local bounty amount of 245 [[Galactic Credit Standard/Legends|credits]].<ref name="Rookies Rendezvous">''[[Rookies: Rendezvous]]''</ref>

